01/05/2011
ZAGREB, Croatia -- President Ivo Josipovic kicked off a four-day visit to the United States on Saturday (April 30th) focusing on bilateral relations, Croatia's EU bid and security issues.
He is due to meet Vice-President Joe Biden and Secretary of State Hillary Clinton on Tuesday.
He will also meet with representatives of the Croatian community in Chicago.
(Hina, Nova TV, HRT - 30/04/11)
